\ls2\ilvl0\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 I don\'92t know how much you know about the Bible but this is pretty much the best thing God can say about you...\uc0\u8232 \
\ls2\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 There isn\'92t a higher standard to aspire for\'85Jesus is not only sinless, perfect, but fully loved and accepted by His father. \'a0\uc0\u8232 \
\ls2\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 And if the next part was written by many modern preachers or scholars who believe in the wrong version of the Gospel\'85the next version would have been\'85And Jesus got a raise, He got a boat for his faithfulness, He found the love of His life and lived happily ever after.\uc0\u8232 \
